title: Christmas GPS
alt: If it's over water, and you can't get a boat or revise the rules to preserve the makeout, there is no helping you.
transcript:
Cueball: Check it out - I got a GPS receiver for Christmas! What should we do with it?Megan: Let's take our latitude & longitude, put our birthdays after the decimal points, then go to that spot and make out.[Cueball is in love.]Merry Christmas from XKCD[sic]
[Car driving off in to the distance.]
